<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich,</ex></expan> als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von Friczen
                                <expan>Sarwürcht<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> und des <expan>Hailman<ex>n</ex>s,</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>, etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> den
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Hailman für uns besant und
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu rede geseczt. Der hat uns
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, daz er des
                                <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>Fricze<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Sarwürcht<ex>en</ex></expan> guts nicht innenhab. Wie
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> dewcht
                            <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>Fricze<ex>n</ex></expan> Sarwürcht, daz er
                            <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> zu dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>Hailma<ex>n</ex></expan> icht zu <expan>sprech<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        hett, so <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir im oder
                            <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>scheinbott<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>voll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gwalt <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        slewnigs <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> von
                            <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>Hailma<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan> vor des reichs
                            <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns zu
                            <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>, wenn wir des ermant
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den,</expan> so <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
                        Hailman anheim ist, on <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>. Denn wo wir ewch
                        lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>. </ab>
